translation.Name: Rio Note - Military #2
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_0: The road blockade has been set up, now nothing gets in or out the city by this side without us knowing, even those red eyed zombies wont be able to get through us!
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_1: And I'm gonna make sure those Exterminator pests doesn't show up any time soon, we've got firepower, what do they have? Bows? Ha!
